msgid "5G Network exception handling: This function detects the connection to the destination IP address every 5 or 90 seconds(Depends on the time required for network registration). If the Ping the destination IP address is not successful, After the network exceeds the abnormal number, switch SIM card."
msgstr "5G 网络异常处理：开启功能后将每隔5-90s(取决于网络注册所需时间)检测一次目标IP地址。如果超出异常次数后仍然无法PING通目标IP地址，会切换SIM卡。"

msgid "4G Network Abnormal Handler"
msgstr "4G 网络异常处理"

msgid "4G Network exception handling: This function detects the connection to the destination IP address every 5 or 90 seconds(Depends on the time required for network registration). If the Ping the destination IP address is not successful, After the network exceeds the abnormal number, switch SIM card."
msgstr "4G 网络异常处理：开启功能后将每隔5-90s(取决于网络注册所需时间)检测一次目标IP地址。如果超出异常次数后仍然无法PING通目标IP地址，会切换SIM卡。"

